:"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25822,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/28\/allah-in-front-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25820,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Allah in front of you when praying","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you is in prayer, let him not spit in front of himself, for Allah is in front of him as he prays.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 398, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 547 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14165,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/13\/something-happens-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25820,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: If something happens during the prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGlorification of Allah is for men and clapping is for women.\u201d Ibn al-Muthna added, \"If something happens in prayer.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1145, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 423 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},